<title>Táńir meni jaratty РӘЖ293</title>
<time_sig>3/4</time_sig>
<key>D</key>
<lyrics>[V1]
.D     A    G    A
 Táńir meni jaratty,
.G     A  D
 soǵan qýanam!

[C1]
.  D          G        A
   Men, sendermen birgemin!
.  A          D        Bm
   Men, sendermen birgemin!
.  Bm         Em       A
   Men, sendermen birgemin!
.  A     D
   Dedi Isa!

[V2]
 Qorqynysh pen túnekten,
 Isa saqtaıdy!

[V3]
 Senem árqashan Isa,
 menimen birge!

[V4]
 Keshirdi Ol kúnámdi,
 Meni qutqardy!

[V5]
 Madaqtaımyn Isany ,
 bar júregimmen!</lyrics>
</song>